losed one of the major exchanges through which it istraded.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe website of Tokyo-based Mt.Gox - which allows Bitcoin to be traded forUS dollars - was shut down today after it had already halted cash <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/withdrawal\" target=\"_blank\">withdrawal</a>s in the wake of rumours that hackers had managed to steal 745,000 Bitcoin.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe crisis at Mt.Gox will raise questions over the future of Bitcoin,which had surged in value last year and attracted the global attention ofmainstream businesses and investors.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">在一起涉嫌价值3亿7千5百万美元的虚拟货币盗窃案件之后，比特币的信誉惨遭重创。此</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">次案发也使得（比特币）主要交易所之一关门倒闭。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">总部位于东京的Mt.Gox是一家经营比特币兑换美元交易的网站。在一则黑客成功盗取了74万4千比特币的传闻之后，它被迫关闭。在此之前，网站已终止了所有提取现金的行为。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">这次发生在Mt.Gox上的危机将对比特币的未来发起许多质疑。自从去年，比特币的价格曾经一路猛涨，并且受到了来自全球主流商家和投资者的关注。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">在价值3.75亿美元的比特币被盗取之后，这种虚拟货币深陷信用危机，交易比特币的几家大型交易所中也有一家已经关闭。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">东京总部的Mt.Gox网站（允许用美元兑换比特币）在&ldquo;黑客盗取745,000个比特币&rdquo;这一流言传出后已经暂停现金提取业务并最终关闭网站。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">比特币在去年刚刚经历价值飙升，并吸引了全球主流企业和投资者的关注，Mt.Gox的这一危机引出了关于比特币的未来的诸多问题。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/883340/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588100/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588100\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p586938/\">沪江网爆笑解读《时间去哪儿了》</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588368/\">英媒发全球大学排行：哈佛第一 清华北大上榜</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588378/\">马航失联班机或折返：雷达发现飞机改变飞行路径</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588711/\">外交部长王毅就外交政策答中外记者问（双语）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p587653/\">有爱爸爸：为儿子精心拍摄土豆人偶婚纱照</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"htt